#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/grid/reykjanes.rst:29
msgid ""
"The sample data is taken from a Met Office NAME Model time-series simulation"
" of the Icelandic Reykjanes Peninsula eruption on 29 May 2024."
msgstr ""

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/grid/reykjanes.rst:32
msgid ""
"A structured grid of cubic voxels is constructed for the 1D spatial "
"coordinates and then thresholded to reveal the underlying volcanic plume of "
"Sulphur Dioxide Air Concentration."
msgstr ""

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/grid/reykjanes.rst:36
msgid ""
"The visualization is enhanced by rendering with a log scale colormap due to "
"the relatively large dynamic range and non-symmetric, skewed distribution of"
" concentration levels within the plume."
msgstr ""

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/grid/reykjanes.rst:40
msgid ""
"The cited release location of the eruption on the peninsula is marked, "
"highlighting the volcanic plume's eastward transport and southerly "
"dispersion."
msgstr ""

